How to Navigate this Notice
This Privacy Notice is divided into several parts, including separate notices for our general business operations and our applications and services, referred to as our Offerings. All notices will provide you with information about what personal data we collect, how we collect it, why we collect it, how we use it, who we share it with, how we protect it, and how long we keep it.
Section
Contains
Read This When
Section
Privacy Notice Homepage
Contains
Information on who we are, how we protect your information, your rights and communication choices, children's privacy, information for certain U.S. state residents (including California), and how to contact us.
Read This When
You give your personal data to Smartsheet, either directly or through use of our applications and services.
Section
General Privacy Notice
Contains
Information on where we process personal data through our Site, social media properties, through pre-contractual activities, during events, through surveys, or in any other interactions with you outside of your use of the Offerings.
Read This When
You visit our Site, you are a current or prospective customer, you are a user of our applications or services, or when you give your personal data to Smartsheet.
This page does not apply to any of the content you enter into the Offerings or Customer Content.
